258
00:18:18,063 --> 00:18:20,365
Nothing will change now.

259
00:18:23,135 --> 00:18:25,003
Anyway, about the incident in Funabashi--

260
00:18:36,181 --> 00:18:38,884
Why make him confess?

261
00:18:39,885 --> 00:18:41,253
SERIES OF RAPE IN CHIBA

262
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:43,088
ITOI FAMILY MURDERS
CHIBA PREFECTURE

263
00:18:47,159 --> 00:18:49,895
The Itoi family murders
happened in Chiba as well.

264
00:18:55,134 --> 00:18:56,535
<i>Up until now,</i>

265
00:18:57,136 --> 00:19:00,439
<i>Mr. Akizumi has never chosen cases
solely for the client's defense.</i>

266
00:19:01,106 --> 00:19:04,143
<i>In many cases, including those
involving Mr. Hiyama and Shoichiro,</i>

267
00:19:04,209 --> 00:19:06,078
<i>he's remained steadfast in his beliefs.</i>

268
00:19:06,778 --> 00:19:08,180
<i>With this case,</i>

269
00:19:08,247 --> 00:19:11,350
<i>he went as far as threatening
another attorney to secure it.</i>

270
00:19:12,284 --> 00:19:13,952
<i>Is he planning something again?</i>

271
00:19:18,056 --> 00:19:19,191
Still working?

272
00:19:19,258 --> 00:19:20,092
YUSAKU SHIMIZU

273
00:19:22,261 --> 00:19:25,631
I've been looking into what I can do
until Mr. Matsunaga's retrial.

274
00:19:25,697 --> 00:19:27,533
I see. Good luck.

275
00:19:27,599 --> 00:19:28,433
Thanks.

276
00:19:41,413 --> 00:19:43,315
My own path, huh?

277
00:19:46,351 --> 00:19:47,219
<i>It seems…</i>

278
00:19:48,253 --> 00:19:50,155
Mr. Akamine is beginning to catch on.

279
00:19:50,822 --> 00:19:52,457
But it's not time yet, right?

280
00:19:53,792 --> 00:19:54,626
No.

281
00:19:55,427 --> 00:19:57,329
This case might be the crisis.

282
00:19:58,530 --> 00:19:59,398
Right.

283
00:19:59,464 --> 00:20:01,433
So keep pretending

284
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,302
like you're oblivious to everything.

285
00:20:06,038 --> 00:20:07,039
Understood.

286
00:20:31,029 --> 00:20:32,297
Mr. Matsunaga.

287
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:36,568
Just a little longer.

288
00:20:37,936 --> 00:20:39,638
Please wait a little longer.

289
00:20:41,873 --> 00:20:42,708
I will…

290
00:20:51,149 --> 00:20:52,150
prove…

291
00:20:53,418 --> 00:20:54,519
your innocence.

292
00:21:28,754 --> 00:21:32,157
That day, he was drinking
until 1 a.m. as usual.

293
00:21:32,724 --> 00:21:35,460
