294
00:21:35,527 --> 00:21:38,530
The way he looked at women was creepy.

295
00:21:38,597 --> 00:21:41,566
It looked like
he only saw them as objects of desire.

296
00:21:43,635 --> 00:21:47,072
"All women fall in love with me."

297
00:21:47,139 --> 00:21:48,740
He was completely misguided.

298
00:21:49,908 --> 00:21:51,410
Disgusting.

299
00:21:52,344 --> 00:21:54,880
He could actually be quite kind.

300
00:21:54,946 --> 00:21:56,315
When taking out the trash,

301
00:21:57,015 --> 00:21:59,885
